THIRD-PARTY SERVICES:

This software uses the Google Gemini API, which is subject to Google's terms
of service and privacy policy. Users must obtain their own API key and agree
to Google's terms:
- https://ai.google.dev/terms
- https://policies.google.com/privacy

API USAGE:

The software transmits text data to Google's Gemini API for processing.
Users are responsible for:
- Ensuring they have the right to transmit their text data
- Complying with Google's API usage policies
- Managing their own API costs and rate limits
- Understanding that text is sent to external servers for processing

DATA PRIVACY:

- API keys are encrypted and stored locally
- No user data is collected by the application itself
- Text processing is performed by Google's Gemini API
- Users should review Google's privacy policy for data handling details

